						<span class="table_programm__speaker__position">руководитель InfraOne Research</span>
					</span>
					</p>

					<p class="table_programm__speaker">
						<span class="table_programm__speaker__desc">
							<span class="table_programm__speaker__name">Жундриков Алексей Викторович, </span>
					<span class="table_programm__speaker__position">главный аналитик InfraOne Research</span>
					</span>
					</p>

					<p class="table_programm__speaker">
						<span class="table_programm__speaker__desc">
